create docker file 
build a dockerfile from runnig docker container
here is a command, how to build a image using dockerfile 

****************************************************
[node1] (local) root@192.168.0.53 ~/static_web
$ docker build -t prabhu_static_git https://github.com/prabhu9683/Dockerfile_sample.git
Sending build context to Docker daemon   51.2kB
Step 1/6 : FROM  ubuntu
 ---> 2ca708c1c9cc
Step 2/6 : MAINTAINER  prabhu
 ---> Running in bc5d6708feb1
Removing intermediate container bc5d6708feb1
 ---> c7f491494869
Step 3/6 : RUN apt-get update
